metadata.name: Founder Edition Pass
metadata.description:
Benefits of owning NFT CLS-3//88 Founder Edition:


  • Exclusive community


  • Early access to new designs


  • Exclusive secret gift


  • Influence product design


  • Priority access to next FE release


The owner aims to build a small, quality community to share knowledge and enjoy the benefits anonymously. 30 Founders Edition slots have been sold out, and the NFT holders will receive an airdrop and vote on a secret gift to be included in the kit.
